    <note>Deng(1) Weigong [13717] According to ZZTJ, 235.7573, he was a Kuangcheng county resident (in Song, Changyuan county of Kaifeng), which was a county of Huazhou in Tang. Therefore descendant Mi's [13721] documentation, which has him as a Huatai resident, is consistant. He is probably the ancestor of all the Shaxian Deng. He moved here when he was a commander of troops in Xuancheng because of disturbances. ZZTJ, 235.7573, 7574, 7575. XTS, 214.3b-4a.</note>
